Name: Bebok Invasion
About the game: Bebok Invasion is a 2D Platformer shooter with many different abilities. 36 levels of jumping, climbing, dashing and fighting against enemies! Skills are unlocked as you progress through the game (getting shoes at the end of the stage). Features: - shooting - wall jumping - wall climbing - dash jumping
